<div class="title">A Great Journey...</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-7</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=tss&Exact=1">tss</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; tss. "A Great Journey...: An Experience with 2C-T-7 (exp3718)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 8, 2001. erowid.org/exp/3718</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
